metadata.name: Gumiho's Spirit Woods
metadata.description:
In a still and quiet wood a thin fog rolls in.  
The silence breaks with the soft brush of fabric and fur gliding across the mossy forest floor.  
A Gumiho wordlessly moves through the mists and brush.  
Mid-transformation; caught between her state of fox and human,  
She attracts the attention of the sprites and spirits of the woodland.  
In her solitude they follow and watch her with intense curious eyes.  
They've watched her grow up and care for these woods.  
If only she could find someone to, in turn, care and look after her as well.  
As her padded feet touch the cool, dewy grass she slowly becomes a fox again and curls up into her den.  
Her heart dreaming of a love so great it can endure all time along side her own.
